Format 9
Columns                 2
Sides                   1
PageStyle               Plain


Style Standard
	Margin                Static
	LatexType             Paragraph
	LatexName             dummy
	ParIndent             MM
	ParSkip               0.4
	Align                 Block
	AlignPossible         Block, Left, Right, Center
	LabelType             No_Label
End


Input stdinsets.inc
Input stdsections.inc
Input stdstarsections.inc
Input stdlayouts.inc
Input stdlists.inc
Input stdfloats.inc
Input stdcounters.inc

NoStyle Part
NoStyle Part*
NoStyle Chapter
NoStyle Chapter*


Style Section
